<title>USA: Harnischfeger extends Giddings tender.</title>
<headline>Harnischfeger extends Giddings tender.</headline>
<dateline>MILWAUKEE 1997-06-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Harnischfeger Industries Inc said said Monday it extended its $19 a share cash tender for Giddings &amp; Lewis Inc until June 13.</p>
<p>The offer was previously scheduled to expire at midnight on June 6.  </p>
<p>Giddings has previously rejected Harnischfeger's offer as inadequate.</p>
<p>Harnischfeger said it was advised that as of midnight on June 6 approximately 6,287,832 shares of Giddings stock had been tendered and not withdrawn.</p>
<p>Harnischfeger makes and distribution of equipment for underground mining, surface mining, pulp and papermaking, and material handling.</p>
<p>((Reuters Chicago Newsdesk (312) 408-8787))</p>
